1
00:00:00,710 --> 00:00:01,710
No way!

2
00:00:02,330 --> 00:00:03,330
When I came here

3
00:00:04,330 --> 00:00:05,170
This whole situation

4
00:00:05,170 --> 00:00:08,750
For all the trouble I've caused everyone,
I am truly sorry.

5
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:10,880
You don't have a shred of proof, do you?

6
00:00:11,040 --> 00:00:13,580
Since you can't prove
it wasn't plagiarism...

7
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:17,750
Come on. Your head is a little too far
from the floor, don't you think?

8
00:00:18,380 --> 00:00:19,830
Right here, right now.

9
00:00:19,830 --> 00:00:21,250
In front of everyone,
you will write a letter of apology.

10
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:23,540
Want me to read it out loud
for everyone?

11
00:00:23,580 --> 00:00:25,580
I must be crazy.

12
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,790
No matter what you do to me.

13
00:00:27,790 --> 00:00:31,040
Seeing that satisfied look on your face
makes me happy.

14
00:00:31,420 --> 00:00:32,630
The moment I see you,
I can't help myself.

15
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:34,000
I'm just so happy.

16
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,170
I understand.

17
00:00:36,420 --> 00:00:38,790
Well, well. Suddenly
so obedient?

18
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:40,920
Then hurry up
and apologize.

19
00:00:41,670 --> 00:00:42,670
Yes.

20
00:00:43,670 --> 00:00:46,540
If this will make you happy...

21
00:00:46,670 --> 00:00:47,960
I'll do anything.

22
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:51,750
Wait a minute.

23
00:00:52,210 --> 00:00:53,210
This...

24
00:00:53,750 --> 00:00:55,670
Isn't this yours,
ma'am?
